{"tid":2383080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再幫襯藍店百佳豐澤，有更多好嘅選擇","createTime":"2021-01-27T16:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T16:50:16.000Z","uid":215090,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e384639a2620afe62cdbffe6ae8cfdc3b6d32c2","tid":2383080,"uid":215090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"枉大家係咁當誠哥係神咁拜，但長實背後又狂喺CCTVB賣廣告，大家要用行動杯葛百佳、豐澤等等嘅長實系商鋪，要迫使佢地唔再係CCTVB賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0s4JBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0s4JBp.jpg&h=d97d1f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2382764/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2382764/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n其實日資既AEON可以完全取代，逢星期三去AEON超市買野好鬼抵，$3一包熱浪，$20一盒日本蛋，平到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算電器都可以幫襯AEON，豐澤部LG電視賣$9980，AEON賣同一部電視，組合價3件電器都只係$8888，豐澤食水深到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賺埋賺埋拎去CCTVB賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8irtqSd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8irtqSd.png&h=b9b535bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKECjce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKECjce.jpg&h=1055161d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家再推薦其他黃店取代，希望誠哥順應民意唔好再係CCTVB賣廣告"},{"pid":"5c4e7962df2426298d1c25f2055208e49c67fb48","tid":2383080,"uid":252588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3416450b03c2d32533ecb32dddea13b11499f19","tid":2383080,"uid":119639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:17:08.000Z","msg":"呢排aeon星期三無左$20盒日本蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c90dc7c56fec67c86db4dd6149125abf3e6ea7d","tid":2383080,"uid"